N2  - On April 5?7, the Boston Chapter will host a national meeting of TIMS. The central topic of the meeting is ?Management Science and Long-Range Planning,? and the sessions will focus on the impact of this subject to business, and to Government. The meeting will be held at the Statler-Hilton Hotel, in downtown Boston. An appropriate program will be provided for ladies.
