N2  - Arrangements are being made for the conduct of the 14th International Meetings of The Institute of Management Sciences at the Centro Medico in Mexico City, Mexico, during the dates of August 22?25, 1967, inclusive. Abstracts of proposed papers for inclusion in the program are invited. These may be submitted in English, French, German, Russian or Spanish provided they are received on or before January 1, 1967, so that they may be translated into English and Spanish, the official meeting languages, prior to printing. Participation in these Meetings is not restricted to members of TIMS.
